---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Academia Europa — European Professional Education Institution"
  description="Structured, evidence-based postgraduate professional education for experienced practitioners. A European institution for professional mastery."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy-deep text-ivory">
    <div class="container-prose py-32 md:py-44">
      <div class="eyebrow text-champagne-soft mb-8">A European Institution for Postgraduate Professional Education</div>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-ivory text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-[1.02] max-w-5xl">
        A European Institution for Structured Professional Mastery.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-10 max-w-2xl text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-platinum">
        Academia Europa develops evidence-based, expert-led postgraduate professional education for practitioners seeking depth, progression, and lasting authority in their field.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/academies" class="btn btn-light">Explore Our Academies</a>
        <a href="/partnerships" class="btn btn-light">Partner With Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Section eyebrow="Our Approach" title="Beyond Fragmented Learning.">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>In many professions, continuing education has become fragmented — isolated webinars, disconnected lectures, certificates without progression. Academia Europa was created to offer a more structured path: one that helps experienced professionals build mastery through carefully designed learning architecture, expert instruction, and disciplined academic standards.</p>
      <p>We are not a marketplace of courses. We are a European institution shaping a long-term ecosystem of professional education.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Beginning with Veterinary Medicine" title="Veterinary Academy International." tone="ivory">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="prose-editorial">
        <p>Veterinary Academy International is the first specialised academy within Academia Europa. VAI is dedicated to advanced veterinary education, case-based learning, clinical reasoning, and evidence-based professional development for veterinarians and veterinary teams worldwide.</p>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a href="/academies/vai" class="btn">Discover VAI</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="border-l border-champagne pl-8 py-2">
        <div class="eyebrow mb-3">Flagship Direction</div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy-deep mb-3">Veterinary Longevity</h3>
        <p class="text-graphite leading-relaxed">An evidence-aware educational framework for animal healthspan, early detection, preventive intervention, and clinical integration.</p>
        <a href="/academies/vai/veterinary-longevity" class="inline-block mt-5 text-sm tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-champagne">Explore →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Learning Pathways" title="Foundation. Mastery. Leadership." align="center">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      {[
        { t: 'Foundation', d: 'Conceptual clarity and a reliable academic base for structured professional growth.' },
        { t: 'Mastery', d: 'Advanced application, clinical reasoning, and refined professional decision-making.' },
        { t: 'Leadership', d: 'For practitioners who aspire to educate, lead, mentor, and shape their field.' },
      ].map((s, i) => (
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="font-serif text-champagne text-sm tracking-[0.3em] mb-4">0{i + 1}</div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy-deep mb-4">{s.t}</h3>
          <p class="text-graphite leading-relaxed">{s.d}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Academic Discipline" title="Designed for Academic and Professional Review." tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Academia Europa programmes are developed with clear learning objectives, structured modules, documented faculty, evidence grading, assessment design, and review processes. This approach supports CPD/CE alignment and prepares selected programmes for external review where applicable.</p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/academic-standards" class="btn">Read Our Academic Standards</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="A Founder's Commitment">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-5">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-navy-deep leading-tight">
          Education that respects the responsibility carried by experienced practitioners.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-7 prose-editorial">
        <p>Academia Europa was founded by Dr. Soheyl Simaei, a veterinarian and entrepreneur with more than two decades of clinical and leadership experience. His vision is to create professional education that is rigorous, elegant, practical, and meaningful.</p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <a href="/about/founder" class="inline-block text-sm tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-champagne">Read More →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <section class="bg-navy-deep text-ivory">
    <div class="container-prose py-28 text-center">
      <div class="eyebrow text-champagne-soft mb-6">For Professionals, Faculty, and Institutions</div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-ivory text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-tight max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Academia Europa welcomes practitioners seeking structured growth, educators committed to meaningful teaching, and institutions exploring academic collaboration.
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-light">Register Interest</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-light">Contact Academia Europa</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
